<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
    <key>title</key>
    <string>Oback</string>
    <key>items</key>
    <array>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSGroupCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>Oback 设置</string>
            <key>footerText</key>
            <string>OPPO 风格边缘手势返回（roothide / iOS 16.4.1）</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSwitchCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>左边缘返回</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>leftEnabled</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <true/>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>从屏幕左边缘向内滑动，触发返回上一页。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSwitchCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>右边缘返回</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>rightEnabled</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <true/>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>从屏幕右边缘向内滑动返回，部分系统 App（如相机）可能不支持。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSwitchCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>触感反馈</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>hapticEnabled</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <true/>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>到达提交阈值时触发轻微震动，提供操作确认感。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSwitchCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>当前页阴影</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>shadowEnabled</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <true/>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>返回过程中给当前页面叠加投影，增强层叠立体感。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSGroupCell</string>
            <key>footerText</key>
            <string>调节屏幕边缘识别返回手势的宽度范围（8–60 点）。越宽越容易误触，越窄越难触发。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>触发宽度 (pt)</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>triggerWidth</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>40</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>8</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>60</real>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSGroupCell</string>
            <key>footerText</key>
            <string>调节返回时上一页随手势探出的位移比例（0–0.6）。数值越大探出越明显。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>视差位移</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>parallaxOffset</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>0.3</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>0</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>0.6</real>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSGroupCell</string>
            <key>footerText</key>
            <string>调节静止时上一页的最小缩放比例（0.8–1.0）。调小纵深感更强。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>上一页最小缩放</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>previousScaleMin</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>0.92</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>0.8</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>1</real>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSGroupCell</string>
            <key>footerText</key>
            <string>调节返回时覆盖在上一页上的暗色遮罩强度（0–0.8）。越大越暗，对比越强烈。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>遮罩浓度</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>dimAlpha</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>0.35</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>0</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>0.8</real>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSGroupCell</string>
            <key>footerText</key>
            <string>调节松手后完成或取消返回动画的时长（0.15–0.6 秒）。越短越跟手，越长越顺滑。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>动画时长 (s)</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>duration</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>0.32</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>0.15</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>0.6</real>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSGroupCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>返回灵敏度</string>
            <key>footerText</key>
            <string>调节边缘返回的触发灵敏度。两个阈值都越低 → 越容易返回（更跟手，但快速横滑列表时可能误触）；越高 → 越需明显拖动或甩动才返回。建议保持默认，按真机手感微调。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>提交位移阈值</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>commitRatio</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>0.3</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>0.1</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>0.5</real>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>提交速度阈值</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>commitVelocity</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>400</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>100</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>1000</real>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSGroupCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>生效范围</string>
            <key>footerText</key>
            <string>默认关闭 = 全局生效（所有 App 均可边缘返回），仅排除下方黑名单内的 App。开启后改为白名单模式：只有「选白名单程序」里的 App 生效，其余不生效。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSwitchCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>启用白名单</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>whitelistMode</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <false/>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>开：仅白名单内的 App 生效。关（默认）：所有 App 生效，排除黑名单内的 App。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSLinkCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>选白名单程序</string>
            <key>detail</key>
            <string>ObackWhiteListController</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSLinkCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>选黑名单程序</string>
            <key>detail</key>
            <string>ObackBlackListController</string>
        </dict>
    </array>
</dict>
</plist>
